item.description:
"Chime in" from 9 - 10 pm on the phone ...

- with your questions
- to get support and suggestions
- to share your LOA experiences

Paula P ( http://lawofattractio... ) will be facilitating the call.

Once you've registered, you'll get an e-mail confirmation with call-in details.
item.why: The safe yet casual atmosphere of the call is designed for us to share & support each other in applying the Law of Attraction consistently in our lives everyday to deliberately manifest our desires & live in jOY!
